{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cbee789daa","title":"邹鲁与革命","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f82a41f7cd","index":0,"year":1925,"month":12,"day":5,"articleId":"cbee789daa"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji3","name":"毛泽东全集第3卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji3.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b7f9597a97","type":"paragraph","text":"邹鲁与革命","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"cbee789daa"},{"id":"cad2eb46dd","type":"paragraph","text":"（1925年12月5日）邹鲁说：“我们国民党的同志应该觉悟，切不可因人家说旧同志不革命便抹杀一切。若不是我们同志层仆磨起，哪能有民国。若不是讨袁护法讨贼北伐诸役一向无前，哪能有今日的历史。就是共产得意的工作英毁商团，乃需要靠杨刘。打杨刘仍需要靠许梁。即今日之制许梁，又何莫非老同志。”很好！邹先生！就请你革命医！实在没有一个人有本领敢于抹杀革命的老同志！须知单是“有民国”“有历史”是不能算数的，须得现在还是革命，须得将来还是革命。若那老同志杨刘，老同志许菜，我看还是少举例为好","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"cbee789daa"}],"page":{"id":"881c7612c7","publicationId":"maoquanji3","articleId":"cbee789daa","start":157,"end":157}}}},"__N_SSG":true}